      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "INSTANT ACTION (4) has a strong record here with two wins and two placings from six starts. In the money last time at Healesville (19.98) in a Grade 5, finishing a 5.5 lengths third. Looks suited and should go close. ASCEND HIBISCUS (1) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at Shepparton over 390m behind Blue Boy Shiraz (22.87) in a Grade 5 H NP. Was in the money prior to that. Has won two of two starts from this draw. Cannot be left out. PAW MELODY (3) ran well two back scoring a T3 RSTW win in 24.26 then out of the placings at Geelong latest but returns to a course where she has performed well. Can improve sharply here. PAW JANELLE (6) is a last-start placegetter here at this trip - worth considering.",
